import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import { BrowserRouter as Router } from 'react-router-dom'

ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <Router>
      <Route path="/">
        <Home />
      </Route>
      <Route path="/survey">
        <Survey />
      </Route>
    </Router>
  </React.StrictMode>
)
